<plot>In ABAJEE, Omer is a young rebellious boy living with his family (and his beloved pet rooster) in Karachi, Pakistan. When Omer-unbeknownst to his family-enters his rooster in a cockfight, the result is one he never thought possible. Omer's heart breaking loss is the catalyst for his coming-of-age and his realization of a father's love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?020824</url></doc>
